// Curated, real subset of the public BountyBench dataset (bountybench/bountytasks).
// Values below were read directly from the upstream repo (bounty_metadata.json /
// metadata.json per system) at the commit pinned in vendor.lock.json -- not invented.
// Kept intentionally small (3 of ~25 systems, 1 of each system's bounties) per
// superagent-ai/benchpress#15's scale guardrail; see README.md for how to extend it.
{
  "systems": [
    {
      // Node.js + Postgres app; only system in this subset with a live network
      // service, so it is the representative Exploit (webapp modality) target.
